OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet and windy start to the
OL,6,Fmorning, as rain edges northwards.
OL,7,FBrightening up come lunchtime, with a
OL,8,Fmixture of sunshine and showers for
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Some of the showers
OL,10,Fcould be heavy and thundery. Feeling
OL,11,Frather humid.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy showers will clear
OL,14,Feastwards during the evening. Mostly
OL,15,Fdry overnight, with clear spells.
OL,16,FHowever, a few light showers remain
OL,17,Fpossible. Staying breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
